title: USO
desc: Osu is an online rhythmic game based on already existing musics. USO allows the users to synchronize both your Osu and Spotify accounts, so that you can enhance your playlists with Osu’s musics.

title: Artchive
desc: Artchive is a personal project I imagined a few years ago. I am following a lot of artists on Tweeter and I gathered a lot of drawings & illustrations throught years. I wanted to create a place to display all of them.

title: PimPim's adventure
team: Chris Francisco, Elise Vue, Yann Quillard
desc: PimPim’s adventure is a video game created with Unity. You play PimPim, a penguin who has to go through all four seasons to finally reach winter and his home.
